  "texts": [
    "Such an endeavor aims to allow autoencoders to autonomously learn meaningful representations from unlabeled data, reducing their reliance on extensive labeled datasets.",
    "Addressing these aspects could significantly expand the applicability and effectiveness of autoencoders across various real-world scenarios with limited labeled data resources.",
    "Autoencoders have proven effective in preserving the non-linear structure of data due to their deep learning capabilities.",
    "However, they face a challenge in preserving higher-order neighbors in complex datasets.",
    "While autoencoders can address the former concern, they may not inherently handle the latter."
